OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey and potentially
OL,6,Fmurky start in places. Cloud will
OL,7,Fgradually break up allowing some
OL,8,Flengthy spells of sunshine, especially
OL,9,Fin the east. Feeling very warm and
OL,10,Fhumid, especially in the strong June
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA warm evening with some late
OL,14,Fsunshine, however cloud and outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain will spill in from the west.
OL,16,FRemaining humid overnight with some
OL,17,Ffurther outbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
