OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with perhaps
OL,6,Fthe odd spot of rain, however cloud
OL,7,Fwill break up, leading to a bright
OL,8,Fafternoon. Feeling a tad fresher but
OL,9,Fstill warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure builds across the region
OL,13,Fbringing plenty of dry and sunny
OL,14,Fweather. Temperatures increasing by
OL,15,Fday and night with hot and humid
OL,16,Fconditions developing early next week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
